isValid.code:
function isValid(response) {
	return (
		response == 'true' ||
		response == 'Subscribed' ||
		response == 'Unsubscribed' ||
		response == 'Unconfirmed' ||
		response == 'Bounced' ||
		response == 'Soft bounced' ||
		response == 'Soft bounced' ||
		response == 'Complained' ||
		response == "You'll get an integer of the active subscriber count" ||
		response == 'Campaign created' ||
		response == 'Campaign created and now sending' ||
		(/\d+/.test(response) && !(/DOCTYPE/.test(response))) ||
		response === null
		);
}
isValid.name: isValid
